function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	
	idTimueClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(actor_TimuePublic)
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idTimueClone) then
	
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idTimueClone, loc_TimuePotionMaking, "NPC_Walk", false)
		
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idTimueClone, loc_TimuePotionMaking)
		
		Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(idTimueClone, "NPC_F_Base_HTH_Use_EyeLevel")
		
		Hydra.QActorWait(idTimueClone, 1.0)
		
		Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(conv_Timue3b, idActorPlayer, idTimueClone)
		
		Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(idTimueClone)
		
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idTimueClone, actor_TimuePublic, "NPC_Walk", true)
		
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idTimueClone, actor_TimuePublic)
		
		Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(idTimueClone, conv_Timue3b)
		
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idTimueClone, 0.0, actor_TimuePublic)
	
	end
end
